<title>USA: Informix names Finocchio chairman.</title>
<headline>Informix names Finocchio chairman.</headline>
<dateline>MENLO PARK, Calif. 1997-07-31</dateline>
<text>
<p>Informix Corp Thursday named Chief Executive Officer Bob Finocchio as its chairman of the board of directors, replacing Phil White, who resigned his seat on the board.</p>
<p>Last week, Finocchio replaced White as president and chief executive officer.</p>
<p>&quot;Now that we have Bob Finocchio in place as chief executive officer, I agree with the board that the company is best served with one clear leader to take a new view of the company's direction,&quot; White said in a statement.</p>
